’Ů@64d797135fc231170fa00674b9d3a37fcab235c0ebbc96495d3fe70737a33f5eÚuTitle: title: plugin stop
Path: Examples
Content:
Stop the plugin named 
``inc``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin stop inc


```
Stop the plugin with the filename 
``~/.cargo/bin/nu_plugin_inc``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin stop ~/.cargo/bin/nu_plugin_inc


```
Stop all plugins.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> plugin list | each { |p| plugin stop $p.name }


```
